headline: 3 Growth Stocks With Significant Insider Ownership
summary: In the last week, the United States market has been flat, yet it has risen by 14% over the past year with earnings projected to grow by 15% annually. In this environment, growth stocks with significant insider ownership can be particularly appealing as they often indicate confidence from those closest to the company's operations and future potential.
